00:29:52.650 --> 00:29:56.820
to be engaged fully in the
moment, in moment by moment

00:29:56.820 --> 00:29:59.390
day to day kinds
of experiences.

00:29:59.390 --> 00:30:04.920
It was about being fully alive
and being more real and being

00:30:04.920 --> 00:30:07.940
