more vulnerable and allow--

00:30:07.940 --> 00:30:09.580
I was so cool before.

00:30:09.580 --> 00:30:11.050
You have never seen cool.

00:30:11.050 --> 00:30:11.955
I was so cool.

00:30:11.955 --> 00:30:12.610
