oh, my gosh.

00:30:12.610 --> 00:30:13.630
This is not it.

00:30:13.630 --> 00:30:14.660
It's about being warm.

00:30:14.660 --> 00:30:17.080
That's much more important
on the other side.

00:30:17.080 --> 00:30:18.590
And all those things started
