00:31:29.560 --> 00:31:31.950
about much more so.

00:31:31.950 --> 00:31:36.520
And I realized that I was
misreading my yearning and

00:31:36.520 --> 00:31:39.360
numbing it with my
soft addictions.

00:31:39.360 --> 00:31:41.950
And I didn't know to call them
